channel.title: Cant log in/ nulled maybe? help me please
channel.description:
ok so heres the problem, when i log in i get a black screen and it sits there for a minute and then says connection lost. [b]I have port forwarded and everything..[/b] my friends and i have been on all day.. i looked at the message on run after running my server and it showed this
[code]Whip Lash is online port: 43594 ip: Suy.no-ip.biz Connection from 127.0.0.1:50008 [client-1-Odie]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 8 ms] Connection from 127.0.0.1:50009 [client-2-Odie]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 2 ms] ClientHandler: Client null disconnected (127.0.0.1) [/code]
My friends and I can not get in.. i need help (we've been on all day) I have tried shutting down my computer and restarting it and deleting cookies and all that stuff. whats wrong with it? If its nulled how would i fix it?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 07, 2009, 04:43:16 pm[/size][hr]can any1 help?!?!?
